{"tid":1183014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街喇，個10萬聯署必回應係奧巴馬既傑作，特朗普無一次回應","createTime":"2019-06-02T15:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T06:59:24.000Z","uid":230104,"like":65,"dislike":448,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"1f6fc1e87529452846b063cbbc5b6a5f860ca009","tid":1183014,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:17:53.000Z","msg":"有網民於本月15日就《逃犯條例》發起的白宮聯署，至今有逾七萬人參加聯署，香港眾志前立法會議員羅冠聰在fb呼籲網民參加聯署，只要有10萬位網民聯署，白宮就需要回應相關訴求。他舉例指，2003年港府就《基本法》23條立法，白宮發表聲明反對，各國隨後亦相繼發表聲明，認為此舉有助營造更龐大的國際壓力，令林鄭更舉步維艱。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國前總統奧巴馬於政府於2011年設立「We The People」網站，市民可就不同議題開設聯署運動，當聯署在30天內達到10萬個簽名或以上這個目標，白宮會就議題作出官方回應。不過，自美國總統特朗普上台後，有多達七項聯署即使到達10萬人簽名，但白宮在今年1月起已沒有就任何達標聯署回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b333f00f34f16b11575fd452116888cededa01","tid":1183014,"uid":230104,"like":29,"dislike":177,"score":-148,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:19:08.000Z","msg":"等睇空歡喜一場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c645a4df90a891f416a839ffad3e075b07cffb9a","tid":1183014,"uid":63670,"like":383,"dislike":5,"score":378,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:19:42.000Z","msg":"千算萬算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過六月九<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行出黎"},{"pid":"5af30aacf822e9b0b79f4ff7be6dbb997e92c54f","tid":1183014,"uid":125641,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:21:21.000Z","msg":"去Twitter好過"},{"pid":"da44d81fd789f7b8607f10151d74744a0f242780","tid":1183014,"uid":161684,"like":416,"dislike":14,"score":402,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:21:28.000Z","msg":"無事時笑鳩人左膠<br />\n有事時求左膠相助<